<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: </font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-28 10:21:16</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>If he's 30, he blows for a level 30.  When I saw him I was just trying to go sell all my FS weps to the gnomes.  Go past the swinging axe, out of the window room, go left and I saw him flying over the bridge at the next level.<BR>
Only had a 30% mana so I waiting till he flew down a bit so I didn't aggro every gobbo in the zone. Rooted him and nuked away.  It took about 2 and a half of my 418pt DD (Shamans suck at DD =P).  The hardest he ever hit me was for 27, and I got encased in fire a couple times.<BR>
In the end he dropped this belt, I wasn't too thrilled and went and sold my weps...<BR>
<BR>
